  "texts": [
    "Where multiple readings were taken for the same measurement, e.g.",
    "pulse, those values were averaged.",
    "Any features that had more than 50% (MAS) or 55% (ADNI) of values missing were eliminated.",
    "Full details of these transformations can be found in Supplementary Tables S4 and S5 online.",
    "Following data pre-processing the MAS dataset consisted of 251 features (311 after one-hot encoding), of which 21 were categorical, 103 boolean (or logical in R terminology) and the remainder numeric."
